@node Main "DC2Lvl-EMine1"

Short:    99 levels for Diamond Caves II
Author:   allan.tnt@post.tele.dk (Allan Rasmussen)
Uploader: allan.tnt@post.tele.dk (Allan Rasmussen)
Type:     game/data
Version:  1.01 (01-Mar-2003)
Url:      http://home19.inet.tele.dk/acme/

These are 99 classic Emerald Mine levels for @{"Diamond Caves II" link DPro},
should work for both one and two players.

Replay files for one player included.


Difficulty: Medium/Hard.


Install: Start the Leveleditor and click on "Import Levels"
(the disk pointing to a drawer) and specify the file EMine1.dc2.


Authors: All levels done by Allan Rasmussen,
based upon @{"Emerald Mine 1" link Emeraldmine} by Kingsoft.

@endnode
